transcript: Yesterday at 6am I sprayed North 40 with ClearField Herbicide at 18 oz per acre across 22 acres, applicator Sam Reed boom sprayer
Applied fertilizer NitroPlus over 14 acres with spinner spreader, total 1200 pounds
I irrigated pivot 3 for 95 minutes last night
Harvested 4200 bushels corn and hauled to Valley Co-op
Did spray work in south field with fungicide this morning
